Training info

Dataset:

  • 2829 frameless Cinderella Girls cards collected from アイマス シンデレラガールズ カードギャラリー

  • 2205 Starlight Stage character cutouts collected from Starlight DB

Small or noisy images were processed with RealESRGAN_x4plus_anime_6B. Tags generated with SmilingWolf/wd-v1-4-convnextv2-tagger-v2 with a threshold of 0.35. No balancing and tag cleaning.

The data collection error in v1.1 has been addressed.

Training cost: ~15 T4-hours (in addition to v1.1 costs)
